flowchart TD
    A([Change Request]) --> B{Emergency?}
    B --> |Yes| C[Emergency CAB]
    B --> |No| D[Standard Review]
    C --> E[Expedited Approval]
    D --> F[Weekly CAB Meeting]
    F --> G{Approved?}
    G --> |Yes| F1{Finance Impact?}
    G --> |No| I[Return to Requester]
    %% ⚡ CHANGED SECTION - Finance approval path with SLA escalation
    F1 --> |Yes| F2[Finance Approval Request]
    F1 --> |No| H[Schedule Change Window]
    F2 --> F3{Approved within SLA?}
    F3 --> |Yes| H
    F3 --> |No - SLA Breach| F4[Auto-Escalate to Finance Director]
    F4 --> F5{Director Decision}
    F5 --> |Approved| H
    F5 --> |Rejected| I
    %% ⚡ END CHANGED SECTION
    H --> J[Implementation]
    J --> K{Successful?}
    K --> |Yes| L[Post-Impl Review]
    K --> |No| M[Incident Report]
    L --> N([Close Change])
    M --> N